nodes.text: Cannison was a Minister who was married to Mrs Cannison and joined Lord Sargo VenHalgon on a vacation to the Cularin system around the time of the Clone Wars. They landed on Cularin and Cannison, VenHalgon and Worrita went off hunting. However, they were chased up a cliff by a Kilassin. They were eventually rescued by the crew of the Starchaser IV.
